data.description: Are you looking for a country home far away from the hustle of the city, yet close enough to be in town when you need to be? If you answered yes, then welcome to 10105 Isom Ave. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is tucked away under mature trees on a attractive corner lot. These motivated sellers have taken excellent care of their home and are ready to find it's new owners, who will love this home like they have. No HOA, so bring your RV, Boat and all your animals. With a new AC (2023), and a 4 year old metal roof, you can feel cool and secured in your home. This one is sure to sell fast, so call for your private showing today.
